ABU DHABI, United Arab Emirates, January 20, 2022/APO Group/ -- 
                                                        
                            H.H. Sheikh Abdullah bin Zayed Al Nahyan, Minister of Foreign Affairs and International Cooperation, received today a phone call from Shirley Ayorkor Botchwey, Minister for Foreign Affairs of Ghana.



During the phone call, Botchwey expressed her country's strong condemnation and denunciation of the terrorist attacks by the terrorist Houthi militia on civil areas and facilities in the UAE and reiterated full solidarity with the UAE.